      • toString

        public java.lang.String toString()

It includes the deleted state, the name of the client company, the geographical location of the client company, the type of home improvement craftsmanship the client company provides, the company size in workforce, the hourly charge rate of the client company, and the identification of a customer that booked a contract with the client company.
